data.name: label9.Text
data.value: This is an optional feature, if not used a message box will appear on your desktop when an alert condition is met. To send an alert via email or text you will need to sign into a valid email address. This feature requires encryption to be enabled. (This feature currently only works with gmail. You will need to make sure that 'allow less secure apps' is turned on for your gmail account. I would recommend not using your primary email address and creating a new email for this application!)
